/*
You have 20 bottles of pills, 19 bottles have 1.0 gram pills, but one has pills of weight 1.1 gram. Given a scale that provides an exact 
measurement, how would you find the heavy bottle? You can only use the scale once.
*/

SOLUTION:

Get 1 pill from bottle 1, 2 pills from bottle 2, ... , 10 pills from bottle 10.
Measure the weight.
If the weight is 0.1 gram more than 55, then the answer is 1.
...
If the weight is 0.x gram more than 55, then the answer is x.
